      value: 3
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2288444071351035227, guid: e83e83eb254b8fe4a87ef3c5621eb470, type: 3}
      propertyPath: allDialogueLines.Array.data[0].line
      value: Hiya fellas! I recon you're headed out west, huh?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2288444071351035227, guid: e83e83eb254b8fe4a87ef3c5621eb470, type: 3}
      propertyPath: allDialogueLines.Array.data[1].line
      value: I've got some supplies for your journey.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2288444071351035227, guid: e83e83eb254b8fe4a87ef3c5621eb470, type: 3}
      propertyPath: allDialogueLines.Array.data[2].line
      value: I came across some of this stuff while out scavenging for scap metal.
        Yeah, I found a few dead robbers with some loot on them!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2288444071351035227, guid: e83e83eb254b8fe4a87ef3c5621eb470, type: 3}
      propertyPath: allDialogueLines.Array.data[3].line
      value: One of your people said somethin' about heading through the mountains.
        Is that right?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2288444071351035227, guid: e83e83eb254b8fe4a87ef3c5621eb470, type: 3}
      propertyPath: allDialogueLines.Array.data[4].line
      value: Oh, no. You'd best be careful headin' that way. I was out that direction
        when I found the dead robbers. I can't imagine what runnin' into the live
        ones would be like!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2288444071351035227, guid: e83e83eb254b8fe4a87ef3c5621eb470, type: 3}
      propertyPath: allDialogueLines.Array.data[5].line
      value: Y'all be safe now. There's a few goodies in here for you if you encounter
        trouble. Hopefully you don't need it though.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2288444071351035227, guid: e83e83eb254b8fe4a87ef3c5621eb470, type: 3}
      propertyPath: allDialogueLines.Array.data[6].line
      value: If you ever roll back on through here, give me a holler!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2288444071351035227, guid: e83e83eb254b8fe4a87ef3c5621eb470, type: 3}
      propertyPath: allDialogueLines.Array.data[0].speaker
      value: Intro Guy
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2288444071351035227, guid: e83e83eb254b8fe4a87ef3c5621eb470, type: 3}
